narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 111 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 111 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: A standard, and excellent, introduction to Spanish, covering all of the elements of learning a language (speaking, listening, writing, reading). Varied forms of assessment that acknowledges student improvement. Highly recommended -- it meets every day but the workload is quite manageable and you will learn a lot!
A lot of work, but a great class. The time spent on the class was totally worth it!
